First Department,

March, 1942.

(March 6, 1942.) The City of New York, Respondent, v. James A. Deering, Appellant, Impleaded with Another, Defendant. (Action No. 1.)

Order unanimously

affirmed, with twenty dollars costs and disbursements. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Dore, Cohn and Callahan, JJ.
